{"tid":1055560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有份捐錢俾東華既 都係幫兇","createTime":"2019-03-10T15:39:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T23:54:44.000Z","uid":197216,"like":15,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"86c640a9d73f59994c6b965082fd1607acca3bec","tid":1055560,"uid":197216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T15:39:35.000Z","msg":"呢單野 唔針對成個東華三院<br />\n係一定唔會有人認真做野<br />\n<br />\n一開始傳媒只係講校長點衰法<br />\n東華係冇人即刻出黎話調查<br />\n<br />\n到而家風向轉去東華個教育部門有問題<br />\n主席先出黎做場Show<br />\n<br />\n我相信 個風向一涉及到將來既捐款數目<br />\n東華成個董事局先會認真看待呢件事<br />\n<br />\n東華三院每年咁多捐款 咁多利益可以輸送<br />\n可以想像到 每間醫院 中學 小學 幼稚園 老人院 既負責人<br />\n會用唔同手段 瘋狂捽自己班下屬<br />\n<br />\n利申 女友做東華小學老師 真係做到仆街"},{"pid":"1e84550c6098a7c37013ed0b2d66e79a0eb5d576","tid":1055560,"uid":98692,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T16:22:32.000Z","msg":"繼續喺東華小學做嘅老師都是幫兇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7060fa3bd88614480c583e0267978c0a853b7a1","tid":1055560,"uid":197216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e84550c6098a7c37013ed0b2d66e79a0eb5d576","tid":1055560,"uid":98692,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T16:22:32.000Z","msg":"繼續喺東華小學做嘅老師都是幫兇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T16:38:22.000Z","msg":"佢打算走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f9596e9ffb50e162004ffd59fcb193cb05252a8","tid":1055560,"uid":173271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T22:13:53.000Z","msg":"不管你捐不捐, 我就不捐了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e425f66db59ff8ab832ce0c317b08c98609dd97b","tid":1055560,"uid":197216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f9596e9ffb50e162004ffd59fcb193cb05252a8","tid":1055560,"uid":173271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T22:13:53.000Z","msg":"不管你捐不捐, 我就不捐了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sm